    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know the neighbor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was driving to Kolki, Matejko-- I always know it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went this way, and there was very, very strong snow, like, like crystal-- the snow and the-- and the everything, I'm telling you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was walking-- and keep my bottle here, the empty bottle.",
